rica.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Mai 2023) 0aCountry lifezConnecticutzGranby (Town). 0aCountry lifezMassachusettszAshfield (Town). 0aLand settlementzConnecticutzGranby (Town)xHistory. 0aLand settlementzMassachusettszAshfield (Town)xHistory. 0aRural poorzConnecticutzGranby (Town)xSocial conditions. 0aRural poorzMassachusettszAshfield (Town)xSocial conditions. 0aSocial classeszConnecticutzGranby (Town)xHistory. 0aSocial classeszMassachusettszAshfield (Town)xHistory. 7aHISTORY / United States / Colonial Period (1600-1775).2bisacsh1 aGubar, Susan, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertYale University Press Backlist eBook-Package 2000-2013z97831105379940 cprintz978030013922840uhttps://doi.org/10.12987/978030015642340uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780300156423423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780300156423/original  a978-3-11-053799-4  Yale University Press Backlist eBook-Package 2000-2013c2000d2013  aEBA_FAO  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-UCY